                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d843">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.032/3.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Message of President <persName type="from">Diaz</persName> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Mexican Congress</gloss> of April 1, 1911.</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-head" calendar="gregorian"
                        when="1911-04-01">April 1, 1911</date>
                </dateline>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Extract.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>The Government has given special attention and granted certain privileges to work
                    on the Colorado River dikes, which is being done m Baja California territory by
                    an authorized Mexican company.</p>
            </div>
